  "text": "14 That same review indicated many persons with MS were receiving minimal or conflicting advice on exercise from healthcare providers. [CITATION_1] The chronic degenerative nature of MS results in lifelong interactions between patients and healthcare providers, and these interactions may be critical for exercise adoption and maintenance.",
